data.title: @amselysen & @racine.corporation modus operandi: build up a hair-raising tension to its limits before it snaps into an ambush of club ready...
data.meta_description:
57 likes, 2 comments - humidexrecords on June 3, 2024: "@amselysen & @racine.corporation modus operandi: build up a hair-raising tension to its limits before it snaps into an ambush of club ready bangers, delivering a profound cathartic release.

With influences stemming from idm, techno, deconstructed club, and an occasional acid touch, the duo effortlessly blends genres to create new possibilities in the realm of club music.

With their breakout performance at @mutekmontreal 2023, alongside Kyoka, Nadia Struiwigh, and more, A&R have established themselves as strong challengers in the future of dancefloors.

Don't miss this rare occasion to see them LIVE at our 5th year anniversary this Friday June 7 at @sat_montreal !".
